sectionText: The course content and instruction will be delivered using the Compass course management system. There will NOT be a required meeting time but there will be weekly online discussions, lessons, and assignments. All specifics will be outlined on Compass. Behaviorial Sciences course. Topic: Children, Language and Communication Ability. SECOND EIGHT WEEK CLASS. The Department does not wait list. **Please do not contact the instructor and ask to be added to the course if it is full. Continue to check online for openings. No overrides are given to overload the class. The class may appear to be overloaded due to a change in the maximum number of students allowed after registration had already begun.
